Step 1: Preheat oven to 425 degrees F (220 degrees FC).Combine parsley, cheese and lemon peel in small bowl; set aside. Toss asparagus, shallots and Becel(R) Buttery Taste margarine in 13 x 9-inchroasting pan. Roast 15 minutes or until tender. Step 2: Arrange asparagus mixture on serving platter, then top with cheese mixture. Season with freshly ground black pepper if desired. Nutritional Facts Calories (Kcals): 130 % Daily Value Total Fat: 6g Saturated fat: 1g Trans Fat: 0g Polyunsaturates: 2.0g Omega-6: 1.4g Omega-3: 0.4g Monounsaturates: 3.0g 9% 5% Cholesterol:0mg 0% Sodium:85mg 4% Potassium: 543mg 12% Total Carbohydrate: 16g Dietary Fibre: 4g Sugars: 5g 5% 16% Protein: 6g Vitamin A: 25% Vitamin C: 25% Calcium: 8% Iron: 25% Preparation Time: 10 minutes Cook time: 15 minutes Total Time: 25 minutes http://www.becel.ca/en/becel/HeartHealthyRecipes/Side-Dishes/Roasted-Asparagus-with-Parmesan-Gremolata.aspx